name: feeds_by_secuid
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool t_tok_bulk_profile_scrapper.
Tool description: Highly maintain and accurate TikTok API to fetch profiles or feeds in bulk.
API description: Fetches feeds from TikTok using a given secUid.

username.description: The username of the TikTok account.

schematype.description: The schema type for the feeds request.

secuid.description: The security UID of the TikTok account.
